{"tid":1486380,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"就算多左中國人支持和平示威，唔代表d咩！！！","createTime":"2019-08-19T00:45:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T01:48:31.000Z","uid":24597,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"953427b426db10e641423979930125a3c1ff86ec","tid":1486380,"uid":24597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T00:45:08.000Z","msg":"佢地只係我地可以「拉攏」既人<br />\n我地可以幫佢地大腦升級！等佢地支持升級行動，佢地都升級行動！<br />\n並唔等於我地要降級就番佢地！一直和平咁活動！<br />\n並唔等於我地要捨棄勇武！<br />\n係時候設DeadLine！DeadLine後升級！開花！<br />\n政府唔回應五大訴求，一切都係假勝利！<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">永不割席！大家迷失果陣不仿回想下係邊個從乜都無開始一齊行到今時今日！</span>就係咁多位香港既手足義士兄弟姊妹！！唔好為左其他人而我地自傷殘殺<br />\n五大訴求！缺一不可！！！<br />\n因果由國！容港治己！"},{"pid":"f75487d59d8bd5f249d3dbb4498449fb319cd919","tid":1486380,"uid":24597,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T00:47:10.000Z","msg":"唔撚好再講咩唔洗VPN<br />\nFC左係假<br />\n或者得愛國小粉紅，佢地d1毛先可以！！<br />\n就算真係有呢d都係我地爭取先出現！！！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OfKOrYe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOfKOrYe.png&h=211f08c2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5UDLubz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5UDLubz.png&h=a3a17f7c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"426f3d7a67965a9dfe84eb81700fd138edbc22b5","tid":1486380,"uid":24597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T00:48:06.000Z","msg":"醒呀大家！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe3651bdb2ff79a76db6bed934754e63c89cb20b","tid":1486380,"uid":24597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T00:49:12.000Z","msg":"醒呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d2d38a7a50381fcae988d428a5d04784c31b762","tid":1486380,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T00:50:07.000Z","